message.content:
This paper belongs to the sub-categories of AI: Case Based and Neural Networks. 

Case Based: The paper describes the use of a case-based reasoning approach to improve a prototype-based neural network model. The authors propose storing specific instances in a CBR memory system to enhance the classification performance of the neural network. 

Neural Networks: The paper primarily focuses on the use of prototype-based incremental neural networks for classification tasks. The authors also propose a co-processing hybrid model that combines the neural network and CBR approaches.
